scripts.start: npx adsum-client-api download:data --config config.json && npx adsum-rn-map install:assets && node node_modules/react-native/local-cli/cli.js start
scripts.compile:ios: npx eslint . && npx adsum-rn-map install:assets --target=ios && node node_modules/react-native/local-cli/cli.js bundle --dev false --platform ios --entry-file index.js --platform ios --bundle-output ios/main.jsbundle --assets-dest ios/
scripts.compile:android: npx eslint . && npx adsum-rn-map install:assets --target=android && react-native bundle --dev false --platform android --entry-file index.js --bundle-output ./android/app/src/main/assets/index.android.bundle --assets-dest android/app/src/main/res/
